  "title": "INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY CONSULTANT",
  "description": "<p></p><p>About the Project</p><p>This role is part of our strategic transformation initiative, led and managed directly by our organization. The project focuses on designing, developing, and modernizing a suite of software applications that support core business operations and improve user experience.</p><p>Driven by our newly established program governance framework, this initiative is aligned with long-term technology and business goals. It reflects our commitment to building robust, scalable, and future-ready platforms using modern architectures and best practices.</p><p></p><p>Responsibilities</p><p>· Design, code, test, and debug software applications that meet both user needs and business objectives.</p><p>· Develop scalable and high-performance application architectures using modern development frameworks.</p><p>· Work closely with business stakeholders and project leads to gather requirements and convert them into effective solutions.</p><p>· Enhance and maintain existing applications, identifying areas for optimization and improvement.</p><p>· Resolve software defects and technical issues promptly to ensure application stability.</p><p>· Participate in code reviews and enforce best practices in coding, testing, and documentation.</p><p>· Collaborate with cross-functional teams within Agile/Scrum methodologies to deliver high-quality solutions.</p><p>· Maintain technical documentation related to application design, workflows, and deployment</p><p></p><p>Skills/Requirement</p><p>· Proficiency in programming languages.</p><p>· Experience in front end Java script technologies – ReactJS</p><p>· Familiarity with databases (SQL, NoSQL) and data modelling.</p><p>· Understanding of software development methodologies (Agile, Scrum, etc.).</p><p></p><p></p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>By sending us your personal data and curriculum vitae (CV), you are deemed to consent to EVO Outsourcing Solutions Pte Ltd and its affiliates to collect, use and disclose your personal data for the purposes set out in the Privacy Policy available at evo-sg.com/privacy-policy. You acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree with the Privacy Policy.</p><p></p>",
